		<title>Jen Huntley, &#8220;The Making of Yosemite: James Mason Hutchings and the Origins of America&#8217;s Most Popular National Park&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2012/04/20/jen-huntley-the-making-of-yosemite-james-mason-hutchings-and-the-origins-of-americas-most-popular-national-park-up-of-kansas-2011/</link>
