		<title>John Bloom, &#8220;There You Have It: The Life, Legacy, and Legend of Howard Cosell&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2012/03/19/john-bloom-there-you-have-it-the-life-legacy-and-legend-of-howard-cosell-university-of-massachusetts-press-2010/</link>
