		<title>Michael David-Fox, &#8220;Showcasing the Great Experiment: Cultural Diplomacy and Western Visitors to the Soviet Union, 1921-1941&#8243;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2012/01/27/michael-david-fox-showcasing-the-great-experiment-cultural-diplomacy-and-western-visitors-to-the-soviet-union-1921-1941-oup-2011/</link>
