		<item>
		<title>Jay Rubenstein, &#8220;Armies of Heaven: The First Crusade and the Quest for Apocalypse&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2011/11/23/jay-rubenstein-armies-of-heaven-the-first-crusade-and-the-quest-for-apocalypse-basic-books-2011/</link>
