		<item>
		<title>Colin Woodard, &#8220;American Nations: A History of the Eleven Rival Regional Cultures of North America&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2011/11/10/colin-woodward-american-nations-a-history-of-eleven-rival-regional-cultures-of-north-america-viking-2011/</link>
