		<title>Steven Barnes, &#8220;Death and Redemption: The Gulag and the Shaping of Soviet Society&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/crossposts/steven-barnes-death-and-redemption-the-gulag-and-the-shaping-of-soviet-society-princeton-up-2011/</link>
