		<title>Sandy Zipp, &#8220;Manhattan Projects: The Rise and Fall of Urban Renewal in Cold War New York&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2011/09/22/samuel-zipp-manhattan-projects-the-rise-and-fall-of-urban-renewal-in-cold-war-new-york-oxford-up-2010/</link>
