		<title>Ricardo Duchesne, &#8220;The Uniqueness of Western Civilization&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2011/05/13/ricardo-duchesne-the-uniqueness-of-western-civilization-brill-2011/</link>
