		<title>Erik Jensen, &#8220;Body by Weimar: Athletes, Gender, and German Modernity&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2011/04/01/erik-jensen-body-by-weimar-athletes-gender-and-german-modernity-oxford-up-2010/</link>
