		<item>
		<title>Lesley Hazleton, &#8220;After the Prophet: the Epic Story of the Shia-Sunni Split&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2011/02/27/lesley-hazleton-after-the-prophet-the-epic-story-of-the-shia-sunni-split-doubleday-2009/</link>
