		<description><![CDATA[Most Americans could tell you who George Washington&#8217;s wife was. (Martha, right?) Most Americans probably couldn&#8217;t tell you who Thomas Jefferson&#8217;s wife was. (It was also Martha, but a different one of course). They might be able to tell you, however, who Thomas Jefferson&#8217;s alleged concubine was, as she has been in the news a [...]]]></description>
