		<item>
		<title>Ann Fabian, &#8220;The Skull Collectors: Race, Science and America&#8217;s Unburied Dead&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2010/12/17/ann-fabian-the-skull-collectors-race-science-and-americas-unburied-dead/</link>
