		<title>Joe Maiolo, &#8220;Cry Havoc: How the Arms Race Drove the World to War, 1931–1941&#8243;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2010/11/12/joe-maiolo-cry-havoc-how-the-arms-race-drove-the-world-to-war-1931%e2%80%931941/</link>
