		<title>James Fleming, &#8220;Fixing the Sky: The Checkered History of Weather and Climate Control&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2010/10/20/james-fleming-fixing-the-sky-the-checkered-history-of-weather-and-climate-control/</link>
