		<title>Jerry Muller, &#8220;Capitalism and the Jews&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2010/06/25/jerry-muller-capitalism-and-the-jews/</link>
		<comments>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2010/06/25/jerry-muller-capitalism-and-the-jews/#comments</comments>
