		<title>Ruth Harris, &#8220;Dreyfus: Politics, Emotion, and the Scandal of the Century&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2010/06/17/ruth-harris-dreyfus-politics-emotion-and-the-scandal-of-the-century/</link>
