		<title>Heather Cox Richardson, &#8220;Wounded Knee: Party Politics and the Road to an American Massacre&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2010/06/03/heather-cox-richardson-wounded-knee-party-politics-and-the-road-to-an-american-massacre/</link>
