		<title>Audrey Kurth Cronin, &#8220;How Terrorism Ends: Understanding the Decline and Demise of Terrorist Campaigns&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2010/05/28/audrey-kurth-cronin-how-terrorism-ends-understanding-the-decline-and-demise-of-terrorist-campaigns/</link>
