		<title>P. Bingham and J. Souza, &#8220;Death From a Distance and the Birth of a Humane Universe&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2010/04/30/p-bingham-and-j-souza-death-from-a-distance-and-the-birth-of-a-humane-universe/</link>
