		<title>Charles King, &#8220;The Ghost of Freedom: A History of the Caucasus&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://newbooksinhistory.com/2010/03/05/charles-king-the-ghost-of-freedom-a-history-of-the-caucasus/</link>
